\cos\theta=\frac{a^2‎+‎b^2‎-‎c^2}{2ab‎}\qquad\text{and}\qquad\sin\theta=\frac{2n}{ab‎}‎‎‎‎.
r=(a‎-‎b\cos\theta)/c
